I dont really know how to do this whole TikTok thing but i tried to explain the best i can in a short amount of time.
I will be posting more later on in the week to further explain & share our unfortunate journey.
Thank you all so so much for all the support & prayers. I will also be praying for everyone who is battling addiction & for those who love the ones addicted bc that is a whole silent battle all on its own.
Dont forget to tell your people you love them & show them the support they need. Its not easy, but we do it for those we love.
Much love. ü´∂üèº Take care.
#addictionawareness #faith #jesussaves #keeploving #keeppushing #keeppraying #amen
